        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks JJW for his great assistance.</p>
            <p>Discusses sexual selection in birds.</p>
            <p>Sends queries on secondary sexual characteristics of birds.</p>
            <p>Has often marvelled at the different growth of the flowering and creeping branches of ivy.</p>
